DCamProf UI is a GUI application built around DCamProf, a free and open-source
command line tool for making camera profiles by Anders Torger.

The DCamProf engine source code (in engine/) is Copyright (c) Anders Torger
and contributors, licensed under GPL-3.0.

The GUI wrapper code (in src/, scripts/, main.py) is Copyright (c) 2026
DCamProf UI Contributors, also licensed under GPL-3.0.

